-- AIG seeking capital from KKR, Flowers: report
-- 
-- Sun Sep 14, 2008 7:54pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/09/14/us-aig-private-idUSLAU48564820080914

 

 (Reuters) NEW YORK - American International Group Inc is seeking capital from private equity firms Kohlberg Kravis Roberts & Co and J.C. Flowers & Co, Bloomberg reported, citing a person familiar with the situation.  

 KKR and J.C. Flowers met with AIG executives at the insurer's New York offices on Sunday, according to Bloomberg.